Crypt-SDTree - A Broadcast Encryption Scheme
============================================

This library implements a subset difference encryption/
revocation scheme that allows broadcast encryption and
decryption. Please refer to the pod documentation for
details.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

